    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Log Query Builder",
      "type": "text",
      "options": {
        "content": "# Loki Query Examples for Pinjol\n\n## Common Log Queries\n```\n# All Pinjol logs\n{job=\"pinjol\"}\n\n# Error logs only\n{job=\"pinjol\", level=\"error\"}\n\n# Search for specific terms\n{job=\"pinjol\"} |~ \"(?i)database\"\n\n# HTTP requests\n{job=\"pinjol\"} |~ \"(?i)(GET|POST|PUT|DELETE)\"\n\n# Database operations\n{job=\"pinjol\"} |~ \"(?i)(SELECT|INSERT|UPDATE|DELETE)\"\n```\n\n## Advanced Queries\n```\n# Count errors per minute\ncount_over_time({job=\"pinjol\", level=\"error\"} [1m])\n\n# Rate of errors\nrate(count_over_time({job=\"pinjol\", level=\"error\"} [5m])[5m:5m])\n\n# Parse JSON logs\n{job=\"pinjol\"} | json | level == \"error\"\n\n# Filter by time\n{job=\"pinjol\"} | json | timestamp >= now() - 1h\n```\n\n## Useful Patterns\n- `|~ \"(?i)pattern\"` - Case insensitive regex\n- `| json` - Parse JSON formatted logs\n- `| line_format \"{{.field}}\"` - Format output\n- `+= \"label\"` - Add label to results\n- `| drop __field__` - Remove field from results",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 28
